_sText: Gg_cabinwars is my first attempt at a map. I originally did it to give something back to my clan, and it turned out to be a very meditative experience. This map took the better part of three weeks to complete, but I've learned a lot in that short time (figuring out how to embed images into the bsp took a while hehe). I tried to focus on dynamics. That is, a fair amount of cover while retaining multiple access points across the map. Maybe I just read too far into it. Either way, here it is.
